                                         Law Enforcement  Links

                                        Norfolk FBI Agents have established strong partnerships and close
   working relationships with the law enforcement agencies in our
   territory. As a result, several task forces are in place whereby local
   police investigators share information and working space with our
   Agents at Norfolk FBI Headquarters. Listed below are fellow law
   enforcement agencies with Internet links:


                                    LOCAL


             Chesapeake Police

                                      Portsmouth Police

             Hampton Police

                                      Virginia Beach Police

             James City County Police

                                      Williamsburg Police

             Newport News Police

                                      York County Sheriff's Dept.

             Norfolk Police

                                      Suffolk Police

             Smithfield Police


                     Christopher Newport University (CNU)

                     College of William & Mary (W&M)

                     Old Dominion University (ODU)




                                    STATE


                         Virginia State Police

                         Commonwealth of Virginia

                         Virginia's Attorney General




